#: ../shared-faqs/nitrokeys.rst:5
msgid "**Q:** What can I use the Nitrokey for?"
msgstr "**Q:** Kādos nolūkos es varu izmantot Nitrokey?"

#: ../shared-faqs/nitrokeys.rst:5
msgid "See the `frontpage`_ for an overview of supported use cases."
msgstr ""
"Skatiet `priekšējā lapa`_, lai apskatītu atbalstītos lietošanas gadījumus."

#: ../start/faq.rst:11
msgid "**Q:** What are the default PINs?"
msgstr "**Q:** Kādi ir noklusējuma PIN kodi?"

#: ../start/faq.rst:7
msgid "**User PIN:** \"123456\""
msgstr "**Uzīvotāja PIN kods:** \"123456\""

#: ../start/faq.rst:8
msgid "**Administrator PIN:** \"12345678\""
msgstr "**Administratora PIN kods:** \"12345678\""

#: ../start/faq.rst:10
msgid ""
"We strongly recommend to change these PINs/password to user-chosen values"
" before using the Nitrokey."
msgstr ""
"Pirms Nitrokey lietošanas iesakām mainīt šos PIN kodus/paroli uz lietotāja "
"izvēlētām vērtībām."

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:11
msgid "**Q:** What is the maximum length of the PIN?"
msgstr "**Q:** Kāds ir maksimālais PIN koda garums?"

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:3
msgid ""
"Nitrokey uses PINs instead of passwords. The main difference is that the "
"hardware limits the amount of tries to three while a limit doesn't exist "
"for passwords. Because of this, a short PIN is still secure and there is "
"not need to choose a long and complex PIN."
msgstr ""
"Nitrokey paroļu vietā izmanto PIN kodus. Galvenā atšķirība ir tā, ka "
"aparatūra ierobežo mēģinājumu skaitu līdz trim, bet parolei šāda "
"ierobežojuma nav. Tāpēc īss PIN kods joprojām ir drošs, un nav nepieciešams "
"izvēlēties garu un sarežģītu PIN kodu."

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:8
msgid ""
"Nitrokey Storage's PINs can be up to 20 digits long and can consist of "
"numbers, characters and special characters. Note: When using GnuPG or "
"OpenSC, 32 character long PINs can be used but aren't supported by "
"Nitrokey App."
msgstr ""
"Nitrokey Storage's PIN kodi var būt līdz 20 ciparu gari un sastāvēt no "
"cipariem, rakstzīmēm un speciālajām rakstzīmēm. Piezīme: Izmantojot GnuPG "
"vai OpenSC, var izmantot 32 rakstzīmju garus PIN kodus, taču Nitrokey "
"lietotne tos neatbalsta."

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:22
msgid "**Q:** What is the User PIN for?"
msgstr "**Q:** Kādam nolūkam tiek izmantots lietotāja PIN kods?"

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:14
msgid ""
"The user PIN is at least 6-digits long and is used to get access to the "
"contect of the Nitrokey. This is the PIN you will use a lot in every day "
"use e.g. for decrypting messages, for unlocking your encrypted storage "
"(NK Storage only) etc."
msgstr ""
"Lietotāja PIN kods ir vismaz sešciparu, un to izmanto, lai piekļūtu Nitrokey "
"kontekstam. Šo PIN kodu jūs bieži izmantosiet ikdienā, piemēram, lai "
"atšifrētu ziņojumus, atbloķētu savu šifrēto krātuvi (tikai NK krātuve) u. c."

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:19
msgid ""
"The user PIN can have up to 20 digits and other characters (e.g. "
"alphabetic and special characters). But as the user PIN is blocked as "
"soon three wrong PIN attempts were done, it is sufficiently secure to "
"only have a 6 digits PIN. The default PIN is 123456."
msgstr ""
"Lietotāja PIN kodā var būt līdz 20 cipariem un citām rakstzīmēm (piemēram, "
"burtiem un speciālajām rakstzīmēm). Taču, tā kā lietotāja PIN tiek bloķēts, "
"tiklīdz ir veikti trīs nepareizi PIN piešķiršanas mēģinājumi, ir pietiekami "
"droši izmantot tikai 6 ciparu PIN kodu. Noklusējuma PIN kods ir 123456."

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:34
msgid "**Q:** What is the Admin PIN for?"
msgstr "**Q:** Kādam nolūkam ir paredzēts administratora PIN kods?"

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:25
msgid ""
"The admin PIN is at least 8-digits long and is used to change "
"contents/settings of the Nitrokey. That is to say after initializing the "
"Nitrokey you probably won't need this PIN too often (e.g. if you want to "
"add another password to the password safe of the Nitrokey Pro or Nitrokey"
" Storage)."
msgstr ""
"Administratora PIN kods ir vismaz 8 ciparu garš, un to izmanto, lai mainītu "
"Nitrokey saturu/nosacījumus. Tas nozīmē, ka pēc Nitrokey inicializēšanas šis "
"PIN kods, visticamāk, jums nebūs nepieciešams pārāk bieži (piemēram, ja "
"vēlaties pievienot citu paroli Nitrokey Pro vai Nitrokey Storage paroles "
"seifam)."

#: ../shared-faqs/pins.rst:31
msgid ""
"The admin PIN can have up to 20 digits and other characters (e.g. "
"alphabetic and special characters). But as the admin PIN is blocked as "
"soon three wrong PIN attempts were done, it is sufficiently secure to "
"only have 8 digits PIN. The default PIN is 12345678."
msgstr ""
"Administratora PIN var būt līdz 20 cipariem un citām rakstzīmēm (piemēram, "
"burtiem un speciālajām rakstzīmēm). Taču, tā kā administratora PIN tiek "
"bloķēts, tiklīdz ir veikti trīs nepareizi PIN piešķiršanas mēģinājumi, ir "
"pietiekami droši izmantot tikai 8 ciparu PIN kodu. Noklusējuma PIN kods ir "
"12345678."

#: ../start/faq.rst:27
msgid "**Q:** Which drivers/tools can be used?"
msgstr "**Q:** Kādus draiverus/instrumentus var izmantot?"

#: ../start/faq.rst:16
msgid ""
"GnuPG is required for many use cases. It is a command line tool but "
"usually you don't need to invoke it directly but use another application "
"with user interface."
msgstr ""
"GnuPG ir nepieciešama daudzos lietošanas gadījumos. Tas ir komandrindas "
"rīks, bet parasti nav nepieciešams to tieši izsaukt, bet gan izmantot citu "
"lietotni ar lietotāja saskarni."

#: ../start/faq.rst:20
msgid ""
"Don't use GnuPG in parallel with OpenSC or another PKCS#11 driver because"
" both may interfere and unexpected issues may result."
msgstr ""
"Nelietojiet GnuPG paralēli OpenSC vai citam PKCS#11 draiverim, jo abi var "
"traucēt un var rasties neparedzētas problēmas."

#: ../start/faq.rst:22
msgid ""
"Install GPG4Win which contains Gnu Privacy Assistant (GPA) and GnuPG "
"(GPG). Start Gnu Privacy Assistant (GPA) or another application such as "
"your email client to use GnuPG. Advanced users could use GnuPG directly "
"(command line). Please note: The Fellowship smart card is similar to the "
"Nitrokey Pro so that this instructions work Nitrokey as well. In general "
"the official documentation is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Instalējiet GPG4Win, kas satur Gnu Privacy Assistant (GPA) un GnuPG (GPG). "
"Palaidiet Gnu Privacy Assistant (GPA) vai citu programmu, piemēram, e-pasta "
"klientu, lai izmantotu GnuPG. Izsmalcināti lietotāji var izmantot GnuPG "
"tieši (komandrindā). Lūdzu, ņemiet vērā: Fellowship viedkarte ir līdzīga "
"Nitrokey Pro, tāpēc šī instrukcija darbojas arī ar Nitrokey. Kopumā "
"ieteicams izmantot oficiālo dokumentāciju."

