msgstr "Instalējiet `GnuPG 2.1 <https://gpgtools.org/>`_ vai jaunāku."

#: ../start/mac/index.rst:14 ../start/windows/index.rst:14
msgid ""
"Connect your Nitrokey to your computer and confirm all dialogs so that "
"the USB smart card device driver gets installed almost automatically."
msgstr ""
"Savienojiet Nitrokey ar datoru un apstipriniet visus dialogus, lai USB "
"viedkartes ierīces draiveris tiktu instalēts gandrīz automātiski."

